{"lastModified":1760017161187,"uri":"c::18277099312::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWith 1 owner's cabin and 3 double cabins, all with en-suite bathrooms, Amada Mia provides accommodation for up to 8 guests on board.\n\nThere are also crew cabins providing accommodation for skipper, hostess, and cook.\n\nEquipment for this boat includes autopilot, TV, Wi-Fi, cockpit speakers, cockpit shower, air conditioning, heating, full galley equipment, dinghy and much more.\n\nWater toys equipment include S.U.P boards, wakeboard, water tube, water ski, electric scooter and sea bob, so you can enjoy water activities while exploring Croatian coast.\n\nIn the open saloon space and a lot of natural light coming in to the cabins, the interior feels luxurious yet homey.\n\nLet our hostess, skipper and cook pamper you on Amada Mia!","blueprint":{"name":"AMADA MIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5962d920-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::596b1680-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::59883b70-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::59543320-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::5966a9b0-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::59460250-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::59c59290-a838-11ef-ba06-8bbb44286dc2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4e2e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::745f91f0-a838-11ef-80af-89b4dcbfc22d